Ares Management LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 10:21 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Ares Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ares Management LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to government and private pension funds, sovereign wealth funds, endowments, foundations, family offices, banks, investment companies, insurance companies, private corporations and a limited number of high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused fixed income portfolios. It also manages mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in fixed income markets across the globe. It primarily invests in below investment grade tradable corporate debt securities. The firm employs fundamental analysis along with bottom-up approach to create its portfolio. It focuses on managing assets in both ...
Ares Management LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to government and private pension funds, sovereign wealth funds, endowments, foundations, family offices, banks, investment companies, insurance companies, private corporations and a limited number of high net worth individuals. The firm manages separate client-focused fixed income portfolios. It also manages mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in fixed income markets across the globe. It primarily invests in below investment grade tradable corporate debt securities. The firm employs fundamental analysis along with bottom-up approach to create its portfolio. It focuses on managing assets in both the private equity and leveraged finance markets. The firm makes opportunistic distressed and rescue investments as well as straight buyouts. The fund’s all-weather strategy is to either buy distressed debt, provide rescue capital or to negotiate for stakes in middle-market companies. The firm seeks to invest in assets across capital structures, from senior debt to common equity. Within private equity, it seeks to invest the aerospace, defense, building products, business services, consumer products, energy, healthcare, and retail industries. The firm focuses on investing in North America. It seeks to invest in majority or shared control investments. Ares Management LLC was founded in 1997 and is based in Los Angeles, California with 26 additional offices across Asia, Australia, and Europe. Ares Management LLC operates as a subsidiary of Ares Management, L.P.
Detailed Description


